trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects.
A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> object contains <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects that represent user profiles from a data source.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> objeto contém <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objetos que representam os perfis de usuário de uma fonte de dados.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> é retornado a partir de <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos de um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> can be supplied to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete profile information and properties from the data source.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> podem ser fornecidos para o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> método para excluir informações de perfil e as propriedades da fonte de dados.

trans-unit.source: The following code example allows a user to search for profiles using the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir permite que um usuário procure perfis usando o <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> e <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: The user can pass the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> returned by the `find` methods to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete the associated profiles from the data source.
trans-unit.target: O usuário pode passar o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> retornado pelo `find` métodos para o <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> método para excluir os perfis associados da fonte de dados.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new, empty <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.

A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is constructed by profile provider implementers and returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> é construído por implementadores de provedor de perfil e retornado do <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos do <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> classe abstrata.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Para obter um exemplo de um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementação que cria um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para perfis de usuário em um repositório de dados, consulte [implementando um provedor de perfil](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to the collection.

The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> method is commonly used by profile-provider implementers to populate a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> to return from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> método é normalmente usado por implementadores de provedor de perfil para preencher um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para retornar a partir de <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, ou <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> método do <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> classe abstrata.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Para obter um exemplo de um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementação que cria um <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para perfis de usuário em um repositório de dados, consulte [implementando um provedor de perfil](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.target: Esse método usa <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList.CopyTo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> copiar <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objetos especificado <xref:System.Array>.

The array must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in the <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
Copies the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> to a one-dimensional array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" />.
This method uses <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList.CopyTo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to copy <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects to the specified array.
trans-unit.target: Esse método usa <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList.CopyTo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> copiar <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objetos na matriz especificada.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects in the collection.
The number of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O número de <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objetos na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that can iterate through the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
Enumerators only allow reading the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeradores permitem apenas ler os dados na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeradores não podem ser usados para modificar a coleção subjacente.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the profile info collection is thread safe.
Always <see langword="false" />, because thread-safe profile info collections are not supported.
trans-unit.target: Sempre <see langword="false" />, porque não há suporte para coleções de informações de perfil de thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: Application code does not normally use this property.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, o código do aplicativo não usa essa propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo.UserName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to retrieve from the collection.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object in the collection, referenced by the specified <see cref="P:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo.UserName" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object for the specified user name.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objeto para o nome de usuário especificado.

trans-unit.source: If name is not found in the collection, <see langword="null" /> is returned.
trans-unit.target: Se o nome não foi encontrado na coleção, <see langword="null" /> será retornado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo.UserName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to remove from the collection.
Removes the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object with the specified user name from the collection.
The collection is read-only.
Makes the contents of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> read-only.

The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método marcas a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> como somente leitura para que <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objetos não podem ser adicionados ou removidos da coleção.

trans-unit.source: After calling the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method, you cannot change the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> back to read/write.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método, você não pode alterar o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para leitura/gravação.

trans-unit.source: Gets the synchronization root.
Always <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> in Visual Basic), because synchronization of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> objects is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Sempre <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> no Visual Basic), porque a sincronização de <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> não há suporte para objetos.
